    "source": {
      "goCharacterKey": "Wriothesley",
      "note": "Generated from Genshin Optimizer sheets (master) + allStat_gen skillParam. Hit keys match GO target paths; multKey = <hitKey>_mult. Levels: Lv10, except constellation-boosted talents of 4-star characters at Lv13 (C6 assumed). Normal/charged/plunging default to physical unless the sheet overrides the element (infusions are NOT applied). CORRECTED 2026-07-22: skill.enhanced_0..4 (Icewhirl Brand-active normal atks) were storing bare normal-attack mv's, missing GO's own skillFistDmg multiplier layer (libs/gi/sheets/src/Characters/Wriothesley/index.tsx: dmgNode(..., prod(subscript(skillIndex, dm.skill.fistDmg), ...))) -- each enhanced_i = normal_i_mult x skillFistDmg(skillParam.skill[0], Lv10=1.70312). Added passive1.hit3/hit5/lusterDmg: his hidden 'Revelation' passive (unlocked via story content) turns Rebuke: Vaulting Fist (Charged Atk) into a 5-hit combo where hits 3 & 5 deal bonus Stellar-Conduct DMG while under Sandrone's Polestar Field ('Stellar Radiance'), plus a bonus lusterDmg instance after the combo -- all reaction-type (EM-scaling/DEF-ignoring via existing stellarconduct_dmg_ auto-detection), C0 values only (lockedPassive hit3AddlMult_=-0.4/hit5AddlMult_=-0.2 baked in; C1/C2/C6 bonuses NOT modeled). hit3_mult = normal.2_mult(1.328822) x skillFistDmg(1.70312) x 0.6; hit5_mult = normal.4_mult(1.793738) x skillFistDmg(1.70312) x 0.8; lusterDmg_mult = charged.dmg_mult(2.75328) unchanged (fires at full charged-attack mv at C0). Verified byte-for-byte against allStat_gen.json skillParam.Wriothesley (auto/skill/lockedPassive arrays) and the live GO sheet source, not the newer libs/gi/formula rewrite (still a TODO stub for this character).",
